		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />According to Disch's docs, or any document related to MMC6, The WRAM Protection bit is included for certain reasons (Anti-Piracy)
<br />
<br />The reason it did not last: Nintendo felt like they were doing it the wrong way, and MMC6 was a total fail because of that.

		

